Effects of Credit Access - Bankruptcy Months Cutoff (36 month)

08/08/2022

apps <- runQuery(
  " select 
                      ua.upstart_id,
                      ua.initial_requested,
                      ua.raising_amount,
                      ua.decision_status,
                      ua.selected_pricing_output_id,
                      ua.created_at::date,
                      usera.user_account_id,
                      po.id,
                      po.priced_at,
                      po.applied_at,
                      po.created_at,
                      po.dti,
                      po.annual_income,
                      po.general_dq_reasons,
                      crs.pull_date::date,
                      crs.fico_score,
                      crs.vantage_score,
                      crs.cleansed_vantage_score,
                      cr.individual_credit_history_days as credit_history,
                      cr.s0y2_birthdate_ccyymm as birthyear,
                      cr.at01_number_of_trades as number_of_accounts,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_24_months,
                      cr.num_trade_accounts,
                      cr.num_trade_accounts_currently_delinquent,
                      cr.total_num_open_accounts,
                      cr.s207a_months_since_most_recent_tradeline_bankruptcy as bankruptcymonths1,
                      cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy as bankruptcymonths2,
                      cr.at33a_total_balance_of_open_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as total_balance,
                      cr.num_inquiries_past_6_months as inquiries,
                      cr.bc101s_total_balance_of_all_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as credit_card_balance,
                      cr.bc107s_number_of_30_and_60_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del_3060,
                      cr.bc108s_number_of_90_or_more_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del90,
                      cr.g007_number_of_30_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue30,
                      cr.g008_number_of_60_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue60,
                      cr.g043_number_of_trades_ever_90_or_more_days_past_due as any_del_12_months,
                      cr.mortgage_balance,
                      cr.revolving_balance,
                      cr.installment_balance,
                      cr.num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months,
                      cr.percent_of_revolving_credit_utilized,
                      cr.at21_months_since_most_recent_trade_opened,
                      cr.g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent,
                      cr.g301s_worst_rating_on_credit_card_trades,
                      cr.bc34s_utilization_for_open_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as creditcard_utilization
    FROM monolith.upstart_applications as ua
    LEFT JOIN monolith.user_applications as usera
    on usera.upstart_application_id = ua.id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.pricings as pr
    on usera.upstart_id = pr.upstart_id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.pricing_outputs as po
    on po.pricing_id = pr.id
    LEFT JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as crs
    on crs.user_account_id = usera.user_account_id
    LEFT JOIN transunion.credit_reports as cr
    on crs.credit_report_id = cr.id
    where 
    pr.pricing_reason='initial' and
    pr.applied_at::date=ua.created_at::date and
    crs.reason = 'initial' and
    cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy>0 and 
    cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy<100
"
)


apps <- apps[abs(as.numeric(created_at-pull_date))<30]
apps <- apps[!duplicated(apps$upstart_id)]
apps[,funded:=ifelse(decision_status=="funded",1,0)]
apps[,mortgage_pct:=mortgage_balance/(total_balance+1)]
apps[,revolving_pct:=revolving_balance/(total_balance+1)]
apps[,appyear:=year(created_at)]
apps[,birthyear:=as.numeric(substr(birthyear,5,8))]
apps[,borrower_age:=appyear-birthyear]
apps[,credit_history:=floor(credit_history/365)]

1 Discontinuity in 36 months since most recent bankruptcy

funded_mean <- apps[,.(funded=mean(funded,na.rm=T)),by=bankruptcymonths2]
funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(bankruptcymonths2<=36,1,0)]

regs <- list()
regs[[1]] <- lm(funded~D+poly(bankruptcymonths2,2),data=funded_mean)
funded_mean[,predfunded:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]

ggplot()+
  geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=predfunded),color="dodgerblue4")+
  geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=predfunded),color="dodgerblue4")+
  geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=funded),color="dodgerblue2")+
  geom_vline(xintercept = 36,color="gray50")+
  theme_minimal()+
  labs(x="Months since bankruptcy",y="Fraction funded")

2 No discontinuity in other variables

control_vars <- c("fico_score","dti","annual_income","borrower_age","credit_history","total_balance","number_of_accounts","inquiries")
control_var_labs <- c("Credit score","Debt-to-income","Income","Age","Credit history","Total balance","No accounts","No inquiries")

g <- list()
for(i in 1:length(control_vars)) {
  
  eval(parse(text=paste0("funded_mean <- apps[bankruptcymonths1%in% 20:50 & annual_income<200000,.(var=mean(",control_vars[i],",na.rm=T)),by=bankruptcymonths1]")))
  funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(bankruptcymonths1<=36,1,0)]
  
  regs <- list()
  regs[[1]] <- lm(var~D+poly(bankruptcymonths1,2),data=funded_mean)
  funded_mean[,predvar:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]
  
  g[[i]] <- ggplot()+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=bankruptcymonths1,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=bankruptcymonths1,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=bankruptcymonths1,y=var),color="dodgerblue2")+
            theme_minimal()+
            geom_vline(xintercept = 36,color="gray50")+
            theme(text = element_text(size=8))
  
  if(i>=7) {
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="Months since bankruptcy",y=control_var_labs[i])
  } else{
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="",y=control_var_labs[i])
  }
  
}

grid.arrange(g[[1]],g[[2]],g[[3]],g[[4]],g[[5]],g[[6]],g[[7]],g[[8]],nrow=4)

creditreports <- runQuery("
      select
                      crs.user_account_id,
                      crs.pull_date::date as pull_date_t,
                      crs.fico_score as fico_score_t,
                      crs.vantage_score as vantage_score_t,
                      crs.cleansed_vantage_score as cleansed_vantage_score_t,
                      cr.at01_number_of_trades as number_of_accounts_t,
                      cr.at33a_total_balance_of_open_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as total_balance_t,
                      cr.num_inquiries_past_6_months as inquiries_t,
                      cr.bc101s_total_balance_of_all_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as credit_card_balance_t,
                      cr.bc107s_number_of_30_and_60_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del_3060_t,
                      cr.bc108s_number_of_90_or_more_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as cc_del90_t,
                      cr.g007_number_of_30_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue30_t,
                      cr.g008_number_of_60_day_or_worse_ratings_in_payment_pattern as pastdue60_t,
                      cr.g043_number_of_trades_ever_90_or_more_days_past_due as any_del_12_months_t,
                      cr.mortgage_balance as mortgage_balance_t,
                      cr.bc34s_utilization_for_open_credit_card_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as creditcard_utilization_t
    from transunion.credit_reports as cr
    INNER JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as crs
    on crs.credit_report_id = cr.id
    where crs.user_account_id in
      (
        select 
            usera.user_account_id
        FROM monolith.upstart_applications as ua
        LEFT JOIN monolith.user_applications as usera
        on usera.upstart_application_id = ua.id
        LEFT JOIN monolith.pricings as pr
        on usera.upstart_id = pr.upstart_id
        LEFT JOIN monolith.pricing_outputs as po
        on po.pricing_id = pr.id
        LEFT JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as crs
        on crs.user_account_id = usera.user_account_id
        LEFT JOIN transunion.credit_reports as cr
        on crs.credit_report_id = cr.id
        where 
        pr.pricing_reason='initial' and
        pr.applied_at::date=ua.created_at::date and
        crs.reason = 'initial' and
        cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy>0 and 
        cr.s207s_months_since_most_recent_public_record_bankruptcy<100
      )")
cr <- merge(apps[,c("pull_date","user_account_id")],creditreports,by="user_account_id")
cr <- cr[pull_date_t>pull_date]
cr[,monthssinceapp:= round(as.numeric(pull_date_t - pull_date)/(365.25/12))]
cr <- cr[monthssinceapp %in% 10:30]
setorder(cr,user_account_id,-pull_date_t)
cr <- cr[!duplicated(cr[,c("user_account_id")])]
cr[,c("pull_date"):=list(NULL)]
regsample <- merge(apps,cr,by="user_account_id")
regsample[,cc_del_3060:=ifelse(is.na(cc_del_3060),0,cc_del_3060)]
regsample[,cc_del_3060_t:=ifelse(is.na(cc_del_3060_t),0,cc_del_3060_t)]
regsample[,cc_del90:=ifelse(is.na(cc_del90),0,cc_del90)]
regsample[,cc_del90_t:=ifelse(is.na(cc_del90_t),0,cc_del90_t)]

regsample[,cc_del:=ifelse(cc_del90_t+cc_del_3060_t>cc_del90+cc_del_3060,1,0)]
regsample[,pastdue:=ifelse(pastdue60_t>pastdue60,1,0)]
regsample[,fico_change:=log(fico_score_t/fico_score)]
regsample[,new_mortgage:=ifelse(mortgage_balance_t>0 & mortgage_balance==0,1,ifelse(mortgage_balance==0 & mortgage_balance_t==0,0,NA))]

regsample[,D:=ifelse(bankruptcymonths2<36,1,0)]
regsample[,distance_to_cutoff:=bankruptcymonths2-36]

regsample[,application_month:=as.Date(paste0(year(applied_at),"-",month(applied_at),"-01"))]

3 Graphical evidence

control_vars <- c("cc_del","fico_change","new_mortgage")
control_var_labs <- c("Credit card delinq.","Credit score change","New mortgage")

g <- list()
for(i in 1:length(control_vars)) {
  
  eval(parse(text=paste0("funded_mean <- regsample[bankruptcymonths2%in% 20:50 & annual_income<200000,.(var=mean(",control_vars[i],",na.rm=T)),by=bankruptcymonths2]")))
  funded_mean[,D:=ifelse(bankruptcymonths2<=36,1,0)]
  
  regs <- list()
  regs[[1]] <- lm(var~D+poly(bankruptcymonths2,2),data=funded_mean)
  funded_mean[,predvar:=predict(regs[[1]],funded_mean)]
  
  g[[i]] <- ggplot()+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==0],aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_line(data=funded_mean[D==1],aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=predvar),color="dodgerblue4")+
            geom_point(data=funded_mean,aes(x=bankruptcymonths2,y=var),color="dodgerblue2")+
            theme_minimal()+
            geom_vline(xintercept = 36.5,color="gray50")+
            theme(text = element_text(size=8))
  
  if(i>=2) {
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="Months since bankruptcy",y=control_var_labs[i])
  } else{
    g[[i]] <- g[[i]]+labs(x="",y=control_var_labs[i])
  }
  
}

grid.arrange(g[[1]],g[[2]],g[[3]],nrow=2)

4 RDD: Kernal-2nd degree, bankwidth-full sample

formula_rdd <- "poly(distance_to_cutoff,2)|monthssinceapp+application_month|(funded~D)|application_month"
bandwidth = 100

r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("cc_del~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])
r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("fico_change~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])
r[[3]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("new_mortgage~",formula_rdd)),data=regsample[abs(distance_to_cutoff)<bandwidth])

stargazer(r,no.space = T,align = T,omit.stat=c("ser","rsq"),style = "qje",omit.table.layout = "n", 
          dep.var.labels = rep(c("Credit card delinq","Credit score change","Mortgage"),2),
          add.lines=list(c("Month,Months since app","Y","Y","Y","Y")),
          type="text")#

formula_rdd <- "poly(distance_to_cutoff,2)+log(1+annual_income)+dti+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries)+log(1+total_balance)+log(1+credit_history)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+log(1+creditcard_utilization*100)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|monthssinceapp+application_month|(funded~D)|application_month"

formula_rdd2 <- "poly(distance_to_cutoff,2)+log(1+annual_income)+dti+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries)+log(1+total_balance)+log(1+credit_history)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+creditcard_utilization*100)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|monthssinceapp+application_month|(funded~D)|application_month"
